    <summary>Run flatpaks without installing!</summary>
    <description>
        <h1 id="flatrun-run-flatpaks-without-installing-them-">Flatrun: Run flatpaks without
            installing them!</h1>
        <p>Flatrun is a command-line tool that lets you run a flatpak once, without it being
            installed to your system or user installation.</p>
        <h2 id="examples-">Examples:</h2>
        <p>Run inkscape from flathub:</p>
        <pre><code class="lang-shell">flatpak run io<span class="hljs-selector-class">.github</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.ryanabx</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.flatrun</span> -<span class="hljs-selector-tag">a</span> org<span class="hljs-selector-class">.inkscape</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.Inkscape</span>
</code></pre>
        <p>Run a locally downloaded flatpak bundle:</p>
        <pre><code class="lang-shell">flatpak run io<span class="hljs-selector-class">.github</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.ryanabx</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.flatrun</span> -f ~/Documents/waycheck.flatpak
</code></pre>
        <p>Get help for more commands:</p>
        <pre><code class="lang-shell">flatpak run io<span class="hljs-selector-class">.github</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.ryanabx</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.flatrun</span> -h
</code></pre>
    </description>
